document_data.name: Palace of the High King
document_data.mainbody: The '''Palace of the High King''' was a wondrous structure located in [[Caer Callidyrr]] on [[Alaron]] within the [[Moonshae Isles]].
document_data.Description: The spires of the Palace of the High King often stood above the clouds, making them easily visible for ships approaching [[Whitefish Bay]].
document_data.History: The palace served as the seat of power for the High King of the Moonshae Isles.
